<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idef676459-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idef67645a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2018—Subsec. (c)(1). <ref href="/us/pl/115/334">Pub. L. 115–334</ref> substituted “2023” for “2018”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
